  <description>
    <p>
      RivalTune is an easy to use configuration tool for SteelSeries mice, allowing users to customize button mappings, DPI settings, and lighting effects. It provides a user-friendly interface to manage profiles and settings for various SteelSeries mouse models.
      This works by using the open-source rivalcfg library to communicate with the mice.
    </p>
    <p>
      Features:
    </p>
    <ul>
      <li>Toggle RGB lighting with ease</li>
      <li>Choose from many color presets</li>
      <li>Create your own color presets</li>
      <li>Change LED zone colors individually (if mouse supports it)</li>
      <li>Change light effects (e.g. rainbow, breathe, etc)</li>
      <li>Adjust mouse sensitivity (only 1 profile supported for now)</li>
    </ul>
  </description>
